00:56:15.846 --> 00:56:17.226 A:middle
Now, the design principles that

00:56:17.226 --> 00:56:18.836 A:middle
we explored today express

00:56:18.916 --> 00:56:21.126 A:middle
fundamental truths about human

00:56:21.126 --> 00:56:22.616 A:middle
perception and cognition.

00:56:23.516 --> 00:56:25.466 A:middle
They are simple, but powerful

00:56:25.466 --> 00:56:27.536 A:middle
reminders about the true nature

00:56:27.846 --> 00:56:29.376 A:middle
and purpose of design.

00:56:30.206 --> 00:56:31.806 A:middle
They provide a framework for

00:56:31.806 --> 00:56:33.796 A:middle
understanding, and a language

00:56:33.876 --> 00:56:36.136 A:middle
for articulating a design's

00:56:36.226 --> 00:56:38.486 A:middle
strengths and its shortcomings.

00:56:39.446 --> 00:56:41.336 A:middle
My hope is that in sharing these

00:56:41.336 --> 00:56:42.806 A:middle
principles with you today, you

00:56:43.746 --> 00:56:45.496 A:middle
will come away with a clear

00:56:45.496 --> 00:56:48.256 A:middle
sense of how your app's designs

00:56:48.736 --> 00:56:50.966 A:middle
can help to fulfill those basic

00:56:50.966 --> 00:56:53.066 A:middle
needs that we all share.

00:56:53.816 --> 00:56:55.356 A:middle
The need to feel safe.

00:56:55.706 --> 00:56:57.256 A:middle
The need to understand.

00:56:57.526 --> 00:56:59.376 A:middle
The need to achieve our goals,

00:56:59.686 --> 00:57:01.306 A:middle
and the need to experience

00:57:01.366 --> 00:57:02.946 A:middle
beauty and joy.

00:57:04.286 --> 00:57:05.826 A:middle
Now, to be sure, while these

00:57:05.826 --> 00:57:07.146 A:middle
principles are, in many ways,

00:57:07.146 --> 00:57:08.566 A:middle
quite simple, applying them to

00:57:08.596 --> 00:57:09.926 A:middle
your work is not.

00:57:11.156 --> 00:57:12.486 A:middle
Each of these principles could

00:57:12.486 --> 00:57:13.686 A:middle
lead you into different

00:57:13.686 --> 00:57:15.486 A:middle
directions about what you should

00:57:15.486 --> 00:57:17.066 A:middle
do with the design of your app.

00:57:18.116 --> 00:57:20.196 A:middle
Designing is so often about

00:57:20.196 --> 00:57:21.776 A:middle
resolving those differences.

00:57:22.416 --> 00:57:23.896 A:middle
This is something that the very

00:57:23.896 --> 00:57:25.526 A:middle
best designers struggle with.

00:57:26.806 --> 00:57:28.676 A:middle
It is also possible to have too

00:57:28.676 --> 00:57:29.566 A:middle
much of a good thing.

00:57:29.966 --> 00:57:31.376 A:middle
Too much feedback is annoying.

00:57:31.416 --> 00:57:32.896 A:middle
Too much visibility is

00:57:32.936 --> 00:57:33.556 A:middle
distracting.

00:57:33.836 --> 00:57:35.486 A:middle
Too much progressive disclosure

00:57:35.786 --> 00:57:37.596 A:middle
can make work flows inefficient.

00:57:38.336 --> 00:57:39.866 A:middle
So you have to be measured in

00:57:39.866 --> 00:57:41.846 A:middle
your approach, and exercise

00:57:41.936 --> 00:57:43.646 A:middle
judgment and discretion.

00:57:44.696 --> 00:57:46.006 A:middle
And the relevance of each

00:57:46.006 --> 00:57:48.096 A:middle
principle can vary depending on

00:57:48.096 --> 00:57:49.596 A:middle
what kind of app you're making.

00:57:50.606 --> 00:57:52.376 A:middle
Platform. Screen size.

00:57:52.776 --> 00:57:55.556 A:middle
Use case. The experience level

00:57:55.556 --> 00:57:56.356 A:middle
of the people who you are

00:57:56.356 --> 00:57:57.256 A:middle
designing for.

00:57:57.886 --> 00:57:59.816 A:middle
These factors and more should

00:57:59.816 --> 00:58:01.736 A:middle
influence what principles are

00:58:01.736 --> 00:58:03.616 A:middle
most relevant at any given

00:58:03.616 --> 00:58:03.986 A:middle
moment.

00:58:05.076 --> 00:58:06.636 A:middle
Working through this can be

00:58:06.636 --> 00:58:07.266 A:middle
challenging.

00:58:07.996 --> 00:58:09.276 A:middle
No one said that designing is

00:58:09.276 --> 00:58:11.966 A:middle
easy, but I do not want you to

00:58:11.966 --> 00:58:12.986 A:middle
be discouraged.

00:58:13.706 --> 00:58:15.576 A:middle
Designing is a lot easier when

00:58:15.576 --> 00:58:17.926 A:middle
you understand the fundamentals.

00:58:18.666 --> 00:58:20.456 A:middle
Let these principles be your

00:58:20.456 --> 00:58:21.416 A:middle
North Star.

00:58:22.106 --> 00:58:23.386 A:middle
They will guide you toward

00:58:23.386 --> 00:58:25.946 A:middle
making apps that better serve

00:58:26.446 --> 00:58:27.996 A:middle
the human beings that you are

00:58:27.996 --> 00:58:28.876 A:middle
designing for.

00:58:29.776 --> 00:58:31.396 A:middle
And that is the thing that

00:58:31.396 --> 00:58:32.366 A:middle
matters most.

00:58:33.476 --> 00:58:35.406 A:middle
And in turn, the people that you

00:58:35.406 --> 00:58:36.516 A:middle
are designing for will

00:58:36.516 --> 00:58:39.366 A:middle
recognize, on some level, all of

00:58:39.366 --> 00:58:40.846 A:middle
the hard work that you have

00:58:40.846 --> 00:58:41.456 A:middle
